OL,3,CDisability rights group stage rally
OL,4,Cover government's proposed welfare cuts
OL,6,FA demonstration has been held in
OL,7,FDarlington against proposed cuts to
OL,8,Fthe welfare system.
OL,10,FThe rally, organised by Disabled
OL,11,FPeople Against Cuts, was held as
OL,12,FChancellor of the Exchequer Rachel
OL,13,FReeves delivered her Spring Statement
OL,14,Fin the Commons.
OL,16,FShe has announced welfare will be cut,
OL,17,Fwith changes to Personal Independence
OL,18,FPayments (PIP) and universal credit
OL,19,Fconfirmed, along with #500 million of
OL,20,Fextra cuts to incapacity benefit.
