OL,3,CDisability rights group stage rally
OL,4,Cover government's proposed welfare cuts
OL,6,FBut Disabled People Against Cuts says
OL,7,FLabour's planned changes would
OL,8,Fincrease inequality.
OL,10,FSpeaking at the protest, campaigner
OL,11,FJenny Joyce said she had been disabled
OL,12,Ffor 19 years, and due to a recent
OL,13,Fdecline in her health, was more
OL,14,Freliant than ever on benefits.
OL,16,FShe told ITV Tyne Tees: "I think
OL,17,Fthey're going to end up with people in
OL,18,Fhospital because I certainly will - if
OL,19,FI don't keep myself warm, and keep my
OL,20,Fcondition under control. (I'm) very
OL,21,Fconcerned.
