OL,3,CDisability rights group stage rally
OL,4,Cover government's proposed welfare cuts
OL,6,F"I voted Labour in and I'm ashamed to
OL,7,Fsay I did. I'm absolutely horrified
OL,8,Fthat they would do this to disabled
OL,9,Fpeople."
OL,11,FLast week the government announced
OL,12,Fhuge cuts to the benefits system,
OL,13,Fsaying they would save #5 billion by
OL,14,F2030, but now the chancellor has gone
OL,15,Ffurther.
OL,17,FReeves announced a freeze on the
OL,18,Fhealth element of universal credit for
OL,19,Fnew claimants until 2030, after an
OL,20,Finitial cut of 50%.
