OL,3,CDisability rights group stage rally
OL,4,Cover government's proposed welfare cuts
OL,6,FThe chancellor revealed the Office for
OL,7,FBudget Responsibility's assessment of
OL,8,Fthe sums means she had to make some
OL,9,F"final adjustments" to the package to
OL,10,Ffind more savings.
OL,12,FThe other changes announced last week
OL,13,Finclude tightening the eligibility
OL,14,Fcriteria for PIP and scrapping the
OL,15,Fcontroversial work capability
OL,16,Fassessment.
OL,18,FThose cuts sparked significant
OL,19,Fbacklash among many Labour MPs and
OL,20,Freportedly even some cabinet ministers.
