OL,4,Cover government's proposed welfare cuts
OL,6,FThe government says the plans are part
OL,7,Fof efforts to get people back to work.
OL,9,FA Department for Work and Pensions
OL,10,Fspokesperson said: "We have set out a
OL,11,Fsweeping package of reforms to health
OL,12,Fand disability benefits that genuinely
OL,13,Fsupport people back into work, while
OL,14,Fputting the welfare system on a more
OL,15,Fsustainable footing so that the safety
OL,16,Fnet is always there to protect those
OL,17,Fwho need it most."
